name: Air Jordan 1
decription: The latest Air Jordan I release amplifies Nike Air branding and features premium materials, a tonal Wings logo and a luxe Guava Ice shade.

name: Air Jordan XII
decription: On September 12, 1996, MJ travelled to Tokyo with some of the league's best for the Hoop Heroes basketball clinic. In front of 32,000 fans, he showed off his skills in a series of 1-on-1s, challenged one of his teammates to a game of H-O-R-S-E, and took part in a friendly exhibition game against some of Japan's famous sumo wrestlers. The latest Air Jordan XII celebrates the event with a print inspired by the kimonos the wrestlers wore during the game.

name: Air Jordan Xiii
decription: Carmelo Anthony’s greatness was first showcased at one of the best high school basketball programs in the country. It was there he developed his deadly offensive game and drew the attention of the league. With a “Class of 2012” sockliner and his alma mater’s team colors, the latest Air Jordan XIII celebrates the waves ‘Melo made even before he donned his cap and gown.

name: Wmns air jordan iii
decription: Every design concept that hits Vogue editor-in-chief Anna Wintour’s desk emerges with one of two marks: “see me” or “AWOK.” The latter, standing for “Anna Wintour okay,” is one of the ultimate signoffs in the world of fashion, and this special edition of the Air Jordan III is the latest to earn it. Inspired by Anna’s iconic suits and sunglasses, the shoe arrives in an all-new tweed build, with an “Edited by Vogue” keychain.

name: Air Swoopes ii
decription: Originally released in 1997, the Air Swoopes II was the follow-up to WNBA superstar Sheryl Swoopes’ signature shoe. With its unconventional lacing system and showy, vertical Swoosh, it quickly resonated beyond the hardwood. The latest return keeps every detail that made the shoe a stand-out, delivered in the original white, black and red colorway.

name: React element 87
decription: The Nike React Element 87 borrows design lines from heritage runners like the Nike Internationalist, adds reflective graphics and transparent details, then places it all on Nike React technology for an innovative take on everyday footwear. For its latest collection, famed fashion label Undercover adds a dose of bold color and youthful expression for fresh dimension.

name: Air Jordan XVIII
decription: Originally released in 2003, the Air Jordan XVIII was designed to encapsulate nearly every theme that had inspired the signature line, including sports cars, Italian craftsmanship and all-around luxury. Now it returns in a rich suede build, sporting embroidery on the shroud that touts its internal Nike color code.

name: Wmns zoom pegasus turbo xx
decription: Part of the Nike City Ready Collection, the Zoom Pegasus Turbo XX delivers forward-thinking versatility for the run, gym and everything after. Created for women by an all-female design team, it firms up the support of the Pegasus Turbo—Nike Running’s most advanced training shoe—with a higher collar and midfoot overlay.
